      <title>马克龙面临在奥运会结束后任命总理的压力：问答</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/macron-faces-pressure-to-name-premier-with-olympics-over-q-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着奥运会的结束，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙不得不重新面对笼罩法国、使政府陷入困境的政治危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/macron-faces-pressure-to-name-premier-with-olympics-over-q-a</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
